0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
A sports flash briefing created solely for voice controlled devices. FanSided Daily keeps you in the know on NFL, NBA, MLB, NHL, College, Soccer and more!

FanSided Daily brings you a daily take on sports news and from around the FanSided Network - a network featuring over 300 communities dedicated to bringing together fans to share their common passions. Our sites serve as a community for like-minded fans to come together to catch up on the latest news and to discuss their passion.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
